@1 = ~Solve the "skinner" murders in the Bridge District

Aura has identified the strange piece of leather as elephant hide. Certainly difficult to find in this city, although Aura thought that a tanner might be able to get ahold of some.~

@1001 = ~Experto crede

Reese, a Lantanese apprentice that we have encountered, asked us whether we knew about something named 'Titan'. Whether the word is referring to a person or object, I cannot say at the moment.~

@1002 = ~Experto crede

A poisoned man has been suspected to be linked to the mysterious 'Titan' that was mentioned to us before. According to the healer Gilbert, it is supposedly some alchemical concoction which is spreading throughout the poorer districts of Athkatla. He suggests questioning those linked to the black market, or perhaps simply the less law-abiding areas of the city, as to where to acquire some.~

@1003 = ~Experto crede

I have been informed that there have been dealings in Titan in the Graveyard District.~

@1004 = ~Experto crede

I have managed to acquire a sample of Titan, and should bring it to Professor Caridius to be examined.~

@1005 = ~Experto crede

I have learned that the dealers of Titan meet with their distributor in the Bridge District at night, close to the Temple of Helm.~

@1006 = ~Experto crede

The dealers of Titan, upon overdosing on Titan, were painfully transformed into grotesque abominations and attacked us. With no further leads, perhaps we should return to Professor Caridius to see if any progress has been made on a cure.~

@1007 = ~Experto crede

Professor Caridius has informed us that Asclepios is the most likely suspect as the creator of Titan. We must find and deal with him. His apprentice, Gilbert, is the most likely person to know where the man resides.~

@1008 = ~Experto crede

We have solved the case involving Titan, though those responsible for distributing it to the black market, the extremist Lantanese organization known as Interitus, are still at large. We will likely have to prepare for their eventual reprisal eventually.~

